{"title":"我们是文化轻骑兵","authors":["石太瑞"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":11,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是文化轻骑兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔苗族〕石太瑞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是文化轻骑兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕山高路难行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涉过千条江和水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨越万座山和岭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行李肩上挑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣鼓带在身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心为人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要为祖国献青春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是文化轻骑兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗飘飘指行程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"串乡走寨不辞苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心儿连着天安门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自编自演唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一专又多能，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹拉弹唱样样会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义文化送上门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是文化轻骑兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作带在身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云里雾里看得远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风里雨里站得稳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习解放军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习大寨人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表演新人新事情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱英雄工农兵。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}